Real San Luis winner Verano 2002

PROMOTION FINAL

First Leg
; Veracruz               ; 1-1;  Real San Luis

Second Leg
; Real San Luis          ; 3-1;  Veracruz

Real San Luis champions and promoted to First Division.


Promotion/Relegation Playoff

NB: between worst team 1st level (Leon) and financially strong (5 million USD) 
    team 2nd level (Veracruz)

First Leg [May 29]
; Veracruz   ; 3-1; León
  [Carlos Casartelli 13, 44, Fernando Juárez 61; Jorge Toledano 77]

Second Leg [Jun 1]
; León       ; 0-0; Veracruz

León relegated, Veracruz promoted



